	Files:	lib/fusion/object.c (1.12) (+1 -0;)
	
	Added D_ASSERT( object->state != FOS_ACTIVE ) to fusion_object_destroy().
	
	Only objects in state FOS_INIT or FOS_DEINIT are allowed to be destroyed directly.
	
