		gfxdrivers/matrox/matrox_spic.c (1.10) (+50 -74;)
	
	Re-added CRTC2 sub-picture opacity handling.
	Don't touch sup-picture bits of C2DATACTL in CRTC2 code.
	Removed mcrtc2->enabled.
	
