	Fixed "primary-layer" option for fullscreen applications.
	
2003-07-11   dok	20:15:25	Denis Oliver Kropp <dok@directfb.org>

	Files:	docs/directfbrc.5.in (1.24) (+5 -0;)
		src/misc/conf.h (1.38) (+3 -0;)
		src/misc/conf.c (1.63) (+18 -0;)
