2002-03-09   dok	00:00:45	Denis Oliver Kropp <dok@directfb.org>

	Files:	gfxdrivers/matrox/matrox_bes.c (1.16) (+11 -3;)
		src/display/idirectfbdisplaylayer.c (1.25) (+29 -4;)
