2001-10-12   dok	12:24:42	Denis Oliver Kropp <dok@directfb.org>

	Files:	gfxdrivers/matrox/matrox_state.c (1.16) (+4 -4;)
	
	Use video alpha method when modifying destinations alpha channel.
